data.description: Welcome home!!  This is the property you've been waiting for in the quaint neighborhood of your dreams.  This home has gone through some beautiful renovations which includes new paint, new appliances, and many more nice upgrades that gives this home that little extra to make this feel like home.  Let's not forget about that huge three car detached garage that will be a dream for any mechanic or for anyone who likes a little extra space for their prize possessions.  You're going to love warm summer nights on the freshly painted rear deck which adjoins a nice rear courtyard.  This private oasis is perfect for gatherings or enjoying some nice family time together.  Come on by and check this beauty out as this wont last long.
